Some WarGame
------------

In this is a group role playing game, groups of three players compete in making their country as rich as possible during some time interval.
They do this by creating alliances with other teams, going to war and investing in bonds.

The game doesn't really have name. When it was used in "Spejderfesival 2011" it went under the name "Diplomacy, Money and War". If you have tried the game, and have a good suggestion for a name, please contact the authors.
For a list of authers see the AUTHORS file.

The game is free to use and modify by anybody, but the supporting code is available under the gpl only, as stated in the LICENSE file.
